 "html": "<p>Ek het die resep by Mari- Louis  Guy gesien en dit het so lekker gelyk.  Amper soos outydse basaar-poeding wat met Idealmelk gemaak is.  Ek het vir haar die resep gevra en dit beproef.  Voorwaar maklik en heerlik.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://capetown.getitonline.co.za/wp-content/uploads/sites/15/2015/04/Steri-Stumpie-Jelly-Mould.jpg?d68cea\" alt loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Ek gee vir julle stap vir stap hoe ek dit gemaak het. Plaas jou vorm op n bord anders is dit moeilik om dit op te tel.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-002.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2225\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-002-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 002\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>Kry jou vorm en meet met n maatbeker af hoeveel vloeistof die vorm gaan neem.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2226\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-003-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 003\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Verhit n bietjie van die steri stumpie en strooi jou hoeveelheid gelatien oor sodat dit oplos.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-010.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2229\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-010-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 010\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Haal van die hitte af en roer die res van die steri stumpies by.  Gooi in jou houer.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-007.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2227\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-007-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 007\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-013.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2230\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-013-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 013\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>Plaas in die yskas   oornag.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-014.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2231\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-014-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 014\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-020.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2232\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-020-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 020\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>Ontvorm en geniet.  Dis voorwaar heerlik en maklik.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-031.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2236\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-031-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 031\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
